name: Autumn carpets
description:
Continuation of the series "Forest artifacts". I took this photo on November 20, 2021. And this is the end of autumn and the beginning of winter soon. Everything in the forest has finally quieted down and is sinking into sleep. I want you to feel through this photo the damp, cool air, so saturated and even intoxicating that your head is spinning. And enjoy the view of such a wonderful carpet, which the trees created by throwing off their robes.
| 3472x4624 px |
